A beautiful and unique voice, emanating from a beautiful and unique young woman. I suspect she hides under her hat partly because of the negative comments from some music 'critics' who just have to say the first destructive thing that comes into their head. Congratulations Tones, I think you are one of a kind and Australia is lucky to call you 'ours'.
